  "body": "Deleting a release from Kubernetes using `helm delete <release-name>` deletes the RC and Service but leaves the Pods running. Deletion of the RC should typically remove the associated Pods but for some reason this is not happening with `helm`.\n\nManually deleting a RC using `kubectl delete rc <rc-name>` removes the RC and the associated Pods.\n",
